00:03:47.939 --> 00:03:49.829
&gt;&gt; Got enough light?

00:03:49.829 --> 00:03:52.230
&gt;&gt; Yeah, I am wondering if the sun is setting
on us there.

00:03:52.230 --> 00:03:53.439
&gt;&gt; We can turn...

00:03:53.439 --> 00:03:54.439
&gt;&gt; I...

00:03:54.439 --> 00:03:57.590
&gt;&gt; The sun is not only setting on us.

